Adding case studies is one of the most powerful ways to turn a theory course into a real investment education. Students see how markets behaved, where investors made mistakes, and what disciplined investors did differently.

Below are 10 high-value real estate case studies that fit naturally into your units and reinforce the core concepts of the track.

10 Real Estate Case Studies for the Track
